<p><a href="https://twitter.com/COMOWeatherBot">@COMOWeatherBot</a> is a running instance of <a href="https://github.com/FireLemons/TwitterWeatherBot">TwitterWeatherBot</a> configured for Columbia, Missouri. Every 2 hours it tweets a forecast for the near future with a random weather fact. It also tweets weather alerts if there are any. It retweets the St.Louis National Weather Service station because it's the station that also covers the Columbia area.</p>
